    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Bards of the College of Spirits seek tales with inherent power-be they legends, histories, or fictions-and bring their subjects to life. Using occult trappings, these bards conjure spiritual embodiments of powerful forces to change the world once more. Such spirits are capricious, though, and what a bard summons isn't always entirely under their control.</p>\n<h3>College of Spirits Features</h3>\n<p>3rd Level: @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-class-features.W2bk5TXsGSM3YeUl]{Guiding Whispers}, @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-class-features.qcpOFW8htwFxkMKC]{Spiritual Focus}, @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-class-features.grNne75ttOreREDV]{Tales from Beyond}</p>\n<p>6th Level: @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-class-features.2Vu5iLKk8RK0y2W6]{Spirit Session}</p>\n<p>14th Level: @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-class-features.s5OOOo1XLlLHTP28]{Mystical Connection}</p>",
